{"tid":2069753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒乞求外援 體現國安立法急迫性","createTime":"2020-06-18T15:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T15:39:55.000Z","uid":249945,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"35c7bf735a1239769aa79b1d436436b04615797b","tid":2069753,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，及台灣的蔡英文總統，透過視頻，在哥本哈根民主高峰會發言，黃之鋒指北京制定港區國安法的目的，是要切斷國際社會對香港的支持，形容香港情勢十分急迫，呼籲歐盟對北京採取更強硬立場。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐丹麥大使館就黃之鋒及蔡英文參與今次高峰會，提出抗議，指責兩人與會違反一個中國原則，干涉中國內政，是對中國的公然挑釁，使館指，黃之鋒乞求外國干涉香港事務，更體現中方啟動香港國安法立法的必要和急迫性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1313372&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1313372%26csid%3D261_341&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=58dbbf6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1313372&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5856979ecdcecb26dc2b341bd026d8e35f81acf6","tid":2069753,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:37:27.000Z","msg":"我睇睇下drop 咗<br />\n你哋係咪？"},{"pid":"36f2b85553bbd61401ca6d8970f5448bdd68ad67","tid":2069753,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}